definitions.definition: A playthrough of a computer or video game in which the whole game or a select part of it, such as a single level , is played with the intent of completing it as quickly as possible, optionally with certain prerequisites .
examples: In the speedrun of Super Mario Bros. 3 , Anonymous Jones finishes the whole game in just 11 minutes.

main_definition: ( video games ) A playthrough of a computer or video game in which the whole game or a select part of it, such as a single level , is played with the intent of completing it as quickly as possible, optionally with certain prerequisites .
